posting_body: ['1671 Washington St managed by Cornerstone Apartments', 'Bedrooms:', '0', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Square Ft.:', '215', 'Price:', '$1095/mo.', '1671 Washington is the modern-styled building perfect for any single-person.', "With a wide array of studio types, as well as one one-bedroom, this type of housing is great for anyone who's looking to live a little North of the populous Capitol Hill.", 'This wonderful location sits close to the Colorado State Capitol as well as a walkeable distance to the entertaining and popular Cheesman Park.', 'Never you mind where to eat, there are a wide assortment of restaurants just down the street.', "From the Denver-popular bar, Stoney's, to the creative Thump Coffee, you're put directly in the zone for any and all Denver activity.", 'Schedule your tour today!', 'Features:', 'Free WiFi', 'Smoke-Free Building', 'Wood Style Flooring', 'Controlled Entry', 'On-Site Coinless Laundry', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Contact us:', 'To schedule a showing please contact our leasing team at', 'To apply NOW please visit <URL>', 'Nearby Neighborhoods:', "Congress Park, City Park, RiNo, Uptown, Sloan's Lake, Cheesman Park, Highlands, Five Points, Downtown, West Wash Park, Hale, University of Denver, LoHi, Baker, Jefferson Park, Platt Park, Capitol Hill", 'Availability and pricing are subject to change.']
